pageProduct.name: Swisse Beauty Hair Skin Nails Gummies 50 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Beauty Hair Skin Nails Gummies are a delicious beauty nutrition formula, with targeted nutrients to support healthy hair, glowing skin and strong nails from within. These 99% sugar free gummies are packed full of flavour, contain no artificial sweeteners and are scientifically formulated with beauty actives.

Biotin supports nail strength and helps reduce nail chipping and splitting. Biotin also maintains healthy hair growth.

Vitamin C supports collagen production, skin firmness and elasticity.

Vitamin C and E provide antioxidant support to help reduce free radical damage to cells in the body.

Zinc supports healthy glowing skin.

Size: 50 Pack

Warnings

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

This medicine contains 2.34 g maltitol per maximum daily dose and may have a laxative effect or cause diarrhoea.

Ingredients

EACH GUMMY (PASTILLE) CONTAINS: Biotin 1.25 mg; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid) 20 mg; Vitamin E (dl-alpha-tocopheryl acetate) 7.5 mg; Zinc (from zinc gluconate) 2.5 mg.

Directions

Adult Dosage: Chew 2 gummies daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat.
